ank you for your time</p><?php }else{?><p>Want to find out more about our products and services? Then simply use the form below to send us an email. Just remember that email isn't secure, so don't send personal or confidential information. If you wish to make a complaint, please use the form below selecting the "If you wish to complain" option from the drop down menu.</p><h3>Please complete the form below: </h3><?php if($contactError){?><div class="footnotes" style="border-top:solid 1px #FF0000; border-bottom:solid 1px #FF0000; padding:5px 0 5px 0; color:#FF0000"><?php echo $contactError?></div><?php }?><form action="" method="post"><div style="border: dashed 1px #999999; border-left:none; border-right:none; padding:10px 0 10px 0"><label style="width:220px"><span class="astk">*</span>What is your question about?</label><select name="contact-topic"><option selected="selected" value="">Please Select Main Topic</option><option value="Borrowing">Borrowing</option><option value="Savings">Savings</option><option value="Insuring">Insuring</option><option value="Credit Cards">Credit Cards</option><option value="Online Banking">Online Banking</option><option value="If you wish to complain">If you wish to complain</option></select></div><div class="footnotes">Compulsory information is marked with *</div><table id="form-table"><tr><td style="width:30px"><label><span class="astk">*</span>Title</label></td><td><select name="title"><option selected="selected" value="">Please Select</option><option value="Mr">Mr</option><option value="Mrs">Mrs</option><option value="Miss">Miss</option><option value="Ms">Ms</option><option value="Doctor">Doctor</option><option value="Father">Father</option><option value="Sir">Sir</option><option value="Professor">Professor</option><option value="Lady">Lady</option></select></td></tr><tr><td><label><span class="astk">*</span>First Name</label></td><td><input type="text" name="fname" value="<?php echo $fname?>" /></td></tr><tr><td><label><span class=